<HEAD>Truck Rams Car, 2 Children Killed, 5 Adults Hurt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>KINGSTON, N.Y. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A truck crashed into a parked car on the
shoulder of the New York State Thruway and sheared off its roof
Wednesday, killing two children and seriously injuring five adults,
police said.
